#

Classic Hummus

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Middle Eastern

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

DipAppetizerSnack

Description

A creamy and flavorful dip made from blended chickpeas, tahini, and garlic, perfect for snacking or spreading.

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • tahini: 1/4 cup
  • garlic: 1 clove
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • ground cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • water: 2-3 tablespoons
  • paprika: for garnish (optional)
